structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.history: Repealed 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 59, sec. 5. -- Amended 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 83, sec. 15. -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 10, sec. 2; and ch. 37, sec. 2. -- Created 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 82, sec. 4.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Recordation of lien information on registration receipt; assignment or termination of lien.
